@endnode


@node "engleski" "English"


  Introduction
  ------------
  
  This is simple little programm.Many people are using it as disco 
  effect.You must have hardware to use it.You can do it yourself.See
  @{"schematic" system "EOLM:ppshow eolm:eolm.iff"}.
  
  With this software you can programm 50 different subprograms with 20
  lines.Each line control 8 bulbs (8 squares).

  For further informations and registration please contact me at 
               
            e-mail adress:
                           davor.cafuta@fer.hr
@endnode

